				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13866440#post-4840077</guid>
				<title>WHIZ-WHAT-OH-GOD!!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13866440/scp-5787#post-4840077</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 08 Dec 2020 23:20:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>actuatedgear</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3285501</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>*sigh* Nope, yep&#8230;. That&#8230; was one of those things. I feel like&#8230; the D class was too ready to acquiesce here. It seemed inappropriate for what a D-class is, but for the sheer WTFery going on, I can see where you might&#8230; bend the usage a little. This could have been longer, but it had, much like a good philly cheese steak, a decent balance.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
