				<wikidot:authorName>not_a_seagull</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3009022</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The transition into the final log still feels a bit rare, but I've realized I have a problem with this line:</p> <blockquote> <p>(Over the next 10 minutes, D-2392 manages to consume the entire humanoid.)</p> </blockquote> <p>Mainly, the fact that it is an imagery opportunity that's pretty much gone to waste.</p> <p>Other than that, I enjoy the surreal integration of some real-life tradition into the anomalous world. It feels like an episode of <em>Regular Show</em> in that way.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
